com.facebook.litho.sections.debug

Class DebugSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.sections.debug.DebugSection

  • public final class DebugSection
extends java.lang.Object
    A DebugSection represents a section node that created part of Litho's component hierarchy. The purpose of this class is for tools such as Stetho's UI inspector to be able to insert Section information when visualising a component hierarchy.
